# Block 1 — Fundação Backend

O projeto é greenfield (vazio). Bloco 1 cria toda a fundação do backend: API Express + TypeScript, banco de dados com todas as tabelas, auth JWT, RBAC, middleware de auditoria, endpoints essenciais, Docker Compose e NGINX.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend Scaffold (`apps/api/`)

#### [NEW] [package.json](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/package.json)
Express + TypeScript project setup com dependências: `express`, `pg`, `redis`, `ioredis`, `bullmq`, `bcrypt`, `jsonwebtoken`, `zod`, `uuid`, `helmet`, `cors`, `pino`.

#### [NEW] [tsconfig.json](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/tsconfig.json)
TypeScript strict mode, target ES2022, module NodeNext.

#### [NEW] [src/index.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/index.ts)
Entry point: env validation no boot (exit se missing), Express app com middlewares globais (helmet, cors, JSON, requestId), route mounting, error handler, graceful shutdown.

---

### Database Migrations (`apps/api/src/db/migrations/`)

Migrations SQL numeradas, uma por grupo de tabelas, criando todas as 16+ tabelas definidas na Seção 5 do PRD:

#### [NEW] [001_settings.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/001_settings.sql)
Tabela `settings` (singleton) + INSERT com defaults. Inclui ENUMs `plan_type`, `instance_status`.

#### [NEW] [002_users.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/002_users.sql)
Tabelas `users` e `refresh_tokens`. ENUMs `user_role`, `user_status`.

#### [NEW] [003_leads_customers.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/003_leads_customers.sql)
Tabelas `leads`, `customers`. ENUMs `lead_stage`, `lead_source`. Extensão `pg_trgm` para busca por nome.

#### [NEW] [004_conversations_messages.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/004_conversations_messages.sql)
Tabelas `conversations`, `messages`. ENUMs `conversation_status`, `message_direction`, `message_type`, `message_status`.

#### [NEW] [005_products.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/005_products.sql)
Tabela `products` com índices GIN trgm para busca.

#### [NEW] [006_orders.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/006_orders.sql)
Tabelas `orders`, `order_items`, `custom_order_details`. ENUMs `order_type`, `order_status`, `delivery_type`. Colunas `GENERATED ALWAYS` para `total_price_cents`.

#### [NEW] [007_production.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/007_production.sql)
Tabelas `production_orders`, `production_steps`. ENUM `production_status`.

#### [NEW] [008_payments.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/008_payments.sql)
Tabela `payments`. ENUM `payment_status`.

#### [NEW] [009_stock_financial.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/009_stock_financial.sql)
Tabelas `stock_movements`, `financial_entries`. ENUMs `stock_movement_type`, `financial_entry_type`.

#### [NEW] [010_audit_logs.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/010_audit_logs.sql)
Tabela `audit_logs` (BIGSERIAL PK) + **REVOKE DELETE ON audit_logs FROM PUBLIC**.

#### [NEW] [011_automation.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/011_automation.sql)
Tabelas `automation_flows`, `automation_executions`. ENUMs `flow_status`, `execution_status`.

#### [NEW] [012_operator_webhook.sql](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrations/012_operator_webhook.sql)
Tabela `operator_webhook_log`.

#### [NEW] [migrate.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/db/migrate.ts)
Script de execução de migrations em ordem numérica contra o PostgreSQL, com tabela `_migrations` para tracking.

