### Middleware

#### [NEW] [src/middleware/requestId.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/middleware/requestId.ts)
Gera UUID v4 por request, adiciona a `req` e ao response header.

#### [NEW] [src/middleware/auth.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/middleware/auth.ts)
Verifica Bearer JWT, extrai payload (id, role, email), anexa a `req.user`.

#### [NEW] [src/middleware/rbac.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/middleware/rbac.ts)
`requireRole(['ADMIN','ATENDENTE'])` — middleware factory. Retorna 403 se role não autorizado.

#### [NEW] [src/middleware/instanceStatus.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/middleware/instanceStatus.ts)
Verifica `settings.status` no Redis cache. Se `suspended` → 403. Roda ANTES do auth. Exceptions: `/operator/webhook`, `/operator/health`.

#### [NEW] [src/middleware/audit.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/middleware/audit.ts)
Helper para registrar ações de escrita no `audit_logs`.

#### [NEW] [src/middleware/rateLimit.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/middleware/rateLimit.ts)
Rate limiter simples em memória (Map + sliding window), configurável por rota.

#### [NEW] [src/middleware/errorHandler.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/middleware/errorHandler.ts)
Global error handler: formato padrão da Seção 9.1. Nunca expõe stack, SQL, ou secrets.

---

### Routes

#### [NEW] [src/routes/auth.routes.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/routes/auth.routes.ts)
`POST /auth/login` — validação Zod, bcrypt compare, JWT sign, refresh token rotation com httpOnly cookie.
`POST /auth/refresh` — refresh token rotation com detecção de roubo.

#### [NEW] [src/routes/operator.routes.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/routes/operator.routes.ts)
`POST /operator/webhook` — HMAC validation, idempotência, actions (provision, suspend, reactivate, update_plan, decommission).
`GET /operator/health` — status check autenticado com Bearer OPERATOR_WEBHOOK_SECRET.

#### [NEW] [src/routes/settings.routes.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/routes/settings.routes.ts)
`GET /settings` — ADMIN only, retorna config da instância.
`PUT /settings` — ADMIN only, atualiza branding, invalida cache Redis.
`POST /settings/logo` — ADMIN only, upload multipart com validação MIME magic bytes.
`GET /settings/public` — público, retorna company_name + logo_url + primary_color.

#### [NEW] [src/routes/health.routes.ts](file:///home/guimp/Documentos/Orion-CRM/apps/api/src/routes/health.routes.ts)
`GET /health` — verifica DB + Redis, retorna status.

